General Npcs:
=====================================
General NPCs are the most basic npcs. They are the not quest givers but serve other purposes such as info givers, attackers(people that will attack you), guards. 

Shopkeepers may also be under this type. 

They will be found under the npc folder in the sub-directory: General.

Npc File Layout:

Name: 
	Type: Guard, Shop, Attacker, Info
	Location:
		X: 
		Y: 
		Z: 
	Click_Messages:
		1: 
		2: 
		3: 
	Vulnerable: True, False
	Kill_Exp: 
	Guard_Radius: 
	
